      "text": "Rows and Result Size\nRows produced, rows returned, and result size\nhelp detect fanout, poor join selectivity, and\nexpensive downstream sorts or aggregations.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-fbcdbdd812f5",
