      "text": "Tie To dbt\nThe goal is to move from a\nSnowflake query back to the\ndbt model, macro, and lineage\nthat produced it.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 22.5,
      "containerId": "node-c3a776fd62c8",
      "originalText": "Tie To dbt\nThe goal is to move from a Snowflake query back to the dbt model, macro, and lineage that produced it.",
