      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Compiled SQL and Model Files\nOnce you identify the model, compare the\ncompiled SQL with the original model file to\nfind filters, joins, incremental logic, or\nmacros that drove the bad profile.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-761c7b2b4c9e",
      "originalText": "Compiled SQL and Model Files\nOnce you identify the model, compare the compiled SQL with the original model file to find filters, joins, incremental logic, or macros that drove the bad profile.",
